*Šalje* se poruka za zahvalnost uz šalicu kafe. (A message of thanks is sent along with a cup of coffee.)

Ona *šalje* pismo njegovom ocu. (She sends a letter to his father.)

Oni *šalju* pozivnice svojim prijateljima. (They are sending invitations to their friends.)

Ona mu *šalje* poruke svakog dana. (She is sending him messages every day.)

Oni su nam *šaljali* pozivnice za proslavu. (They were sending us invitations for the celebration.)